<h2>Help</h2>

<p>Here you can find the help files that come with the game (accessed using '?'), but in swish online format.  This help is up-to-date for <b>Angband 3.4.1</b>.

<h3>Players' Guide</h3>
<p>If you're looking for strategy and tactics for playing the game, have a look at the <a href="guide">Players' Guide</a> for lots of hints and tips.

<h3>User manual</h3>
<p>There's a user manual that comes with the game, which is more focussed on describing the game in exhaustive detail. Enjoy!

